10 December 2013The memorial service of the late ex- World Boxing Champion and SA Sport Legend Jacob Baby Jake Matlala will be held tomorrow.DATE: 11 December 2013 TIME: 09h00 VENUE: Nasrec Stadium JHBMinister Mbalula, Sascoc Leadership Federation, Boxing Administrator, former and current boxers, will join Mrs Mapule Matlala and the twochildren during the service. Media are invited Issued by: Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)